- Theremin
- music concrete, sampling
- sample the space age
- laser harp, structured light + shaow
- syntax and semantics of performin music?
- ghost busters stream --> ghost busters game demo PS3
	add physical weight and resistance to it.
- Sputnik Satelitenbahnen
- two player live music system, master and apprentice.
	The master controls the score while the apprentice adds the nuances and the expression.

- lasso samples
	samples are drifting by as 3d objects. The player can catch a sample by pointing at it which starts it. If the player drags the in the opposit direction it is rewinded, if she drags it in the direction of the movement the sample is accelerated. 

- "[...] that it only exists when someone uses it."



